Little_Rock.Bechle Apartment Building: The Bechle Apartment Building is a historic two-unit house at 1000 East 9th Street in Little Rock, Arkansas. It is a 2-1/2 story brick structure, with a hip roof pierced by a single hip-roof dormer at its front. The dormer has small windows laid out like a Palladian window, with Stick style decorative elements.
